               <a name="1"></a>
               <h2 class="">Home</h2>

               <div class="contentinner">
                   <!--<img src="images/homebanner.jpg" alt="" />-->
                   <p>Founded in 1992, Pentz & Partners is committed to be the finest full-service, retail oriented real estate firm in the Western United States. We combine honesty, creativity, knowledge, experience, relationships and dedication to achieve each of our clients goals and objectives. We provide a full range of services to many of the nations best retailers, including: site selection, disposition, consultation, acquisition, and property management. Let us put our expertise and personal touch to all of your company's real estate needs.</p>
                   <p class="sig">
                       <img src="sig.png" alt="John C. Pentz Signature"><br>
                       <strong>John C. Pentz</strong><br>
                       President<br>
                       Pentz & Partners, Inc
                   </p>
               </div>
           </div>

           <div class="content" id="c2" style="display: none;">
               <a name="2"></a>
               <h2 class="">Retail Representation</h2>

               <div class="contentinner">
                   <p>Pentz & Partners strives to learn and know every facet of our retail clients business to enable our team of experienced professionals to select the prime available sites, and negotiate the best possible financial terms.</p>
                   <p>As a result, we have developed long-lasting relationships with many of the regions and nation’s most successful retailers. Our commitment to service and results has allowed us to gain new clients as well as cultivate existing relationships.</p>
                   <p>We provide the competitive market assessment your company needs to determine the locations that best suit your demographic criteria and ensure the success of your retailing future.</p>
                   <p>Pentz & Partners not only evaluates the location, visability. street access, market demographics, signage and competitive sales history of each site, but also networks with other shopping center industry professionals to find creative solutions for retailers in a rapidly changing and competitive marketplace.</p>
                   <p>We look forward to learning and exclusively representing your real estate needs.</p>
               </div>
           </div>

           <div class="content" id="c3" style="display: none;">
               <a name="3"></a>
               <h2 class="">Disposition</h2>

               <div class="contentinner">
                   <p>Pentz & Partners has developed a unique niche and creative approach to helping retailers reposition and/or dispose of existing retail sites.</p>
                   <p>Our teamwork in finding timely and innovative solutions at the least possible expense to our clients has brought a large number of national and local retailers to depend upon Pentz & Partners for their disposition needs.</p>
                   <p>Our professionals position your excess properties for quick sale or lease by implementing accurate evaluations of your portfolio and providing creative marketing to retailers actively looking to fill these spaces.</p>
                   <p>Our computer database of over 3,500 retailers can quickly match the needs of these expansion-minded companies to the size requirements of any sized space for disposition.</p>
                   <p>In addition, we strive to work with every party in the transaction, including landlords, thereby minimizing time and expense to our clients. Pentz & Partners has the ability and know how to handle your disposition needs, whether it be one store or an entire chain of stores.</p>
               </div>
           </div>

           <div class="content" id="c4" style="display: none;">
               <a name="4"></a>
               <h2 class="">Consultation</h2>

               <div class="contentinner">
                   <p>Pentz & Partners can provide consultation to every real estate or retail need. Whether your needs are site selection or acquisition, a market or trade area evaluation, disposition of assets, property management, short or long term development strategy, lease negotiation, marketing, legal representation, expert witness, store design or architecture, signage or other retail or real estate related items; Pentz & Partners can provide you with the pertinent information or refer you to those persons or companies who are qualified to assist you in each of the foregoing specialty areas.</p>
                   <p>We only work with those professionals who have the same high standards as we do and who can help our clients achieve these desired results in a time-conscious and cost effective manner.</p>
                   <p>Our consultation services can be performed by the hour, by the job, or by retaining our services if the need is long term.</p>
                   <p>Pentz & Partners goes out of its way to make sure our clients receive the most up to date and knowledgeable information in the market so they can make informed decisions. We can assist your in-house real estate department or, in effect, become your outside source for all of your retail real estate needs.</p>
               </div>
           </div>

           <div class="content" id="c5" style="display: none;">
               <a name="5"></a>
               <h2 class="">Mexico</h2>

               <div class="contentinner">
                   <p>
                       <a href="http://www.theshoppes.com.mx">www.theshoppes.com.mx</a><br>
                       <a href="http://www.mexicodp.com">www.mexicodp.com</a>
                   </p>

                   <strong>The Shoppes at Palmilla</strong><br>
                   San Jose del Cabo, Mexico
                   <p>A luxury Lifestyle Shopping Center of approximately 50,000 square feet with restaurants, jewelry, art, high end clothing and Executive Offices all located at the entrance to the One & Only Palmilla, which has an expansive golf course and ocean views.</p>

                   <strong>Thompson Los Cabos</strong>
                   <p>An opulent 115 room Thompson boutique hotel located on the beach in Cabo San Lucas with a direct view to the famous Arch. The hotel is paired with a 26 unit fractional condominium project that is available for purchase and are designed by JSA Architects and AI Interiores, the project will open in 2014.</p>

                   <strong>Plaza El Faro</strong><br>
                   San Jose Del Cabo, Mexico
                   <p>A 19,000+ square foot Design Center located adjacent to the Palmilla. Opened in 2007.</p>

                   <strong>The Shoppes at Culiacan</strong><br>
                   Culiacan, Mexico
                   <p>Currently under construction, the shopping center includes Lowe's Home Improvement Center, proposed Best Buy, Carl's Jr., AutoZone, Pemex and additional stores.</p>

                   <strong>The Shoppes at La Paz</strong><br>
                   La Paz, Mexico
                   <p>An existing 580,000 square foot regional mall. Only master planned shopping center in the region with Liverpool, Soriana, Home Depot, Cineopolis, C&A, Coppel, 2 Hotels, 6-8 Restaurants, Food Court and Shops.</p>

                   <h3>Miscellaneous Oceanfront Homes - Los Cabos Mexico</h3>

                   <strong>Casa La Roca - Los Cabos, Mexico</strong>
                   <p>6,000 square foot luxury home sold to Leading Residences of the World in March 2005.</p>

                   <strong>Lot 34 - Puerto Los Cabos, San Jose del Cabo, Mexico</strong>
                   <p>10,000 square foot luxury home as part of a master planned community with Marina and Golf Course.</p>

                   <strong>Lot 7 - Pamilla Resort, San Jose del Cabo, Mexico</strong>
                   <p>Planned home of 10,600 square feet as part of existing Palmilla Resort with One & Only Palmilla Hotel.</p>

               </div>
