           <div class="content" id="c6" style="display: none;">
               <a name="6"></a>
               <h2 class="">Property Management</h2>

               <div class="contentinner">

                   <p>Pentz & Partners can provide you with property management for all your fee-owned or leased properties.</p>
                   <p>Through our affiliated property management company, we can maximize the value of your property while increasing its revenue to you and your company.</p>
                   <p>We have integrated our talents to not only provide you with responsive, hands-on, entrepreneurial management and leasing, but also computerized accounting systems that meet the individual property management needs of each client and property.</p>
                   <p>Our list of services include the following:</p>
                   <ul>
                       <li>Evaluation of existing property managemen</li>
                       <li>Site inspections and evaluations</li>
                       <li>Accounting, budgeting, common area billing and management plans</li>
                       <li>Rent collections and legal proceedings</li>
                       <li>Lease review; setup, and administration</li>
                       <li>Reporting and system setup</li>
                       <li>Property tax and insurance administration</li>
                       <li>Physical maintenance and security</li>
                       <li>Marketing, leasing and renewals</li>
                       <li>Tenant improvement, construction and rehabilitation</li>
                       <li>Risk management and preventive maintenance</li>
                       <li>Asset management and investment advisory</li>
                       <li>Landlord and tenant communications</li>
                   </ul>
               </div>
           </div>

           <div class="content" id="c7" style="display: none;">
               <a name="7"></a>
               <h2 class="">Acquisition</h2>

               <div class="contentinner">
                   <p>Pentz & Partners’ intimate knowledge of each market and each of the major retail shopping centers and retailers located in it, has resulted in our ability to acquire individual sites and/or retail chains for our clients.</p>
                   <p>Through our affiliated investment company, we can also purchase sites and develop and/or remodel existing properties to meet our clients expansion requirements. We not only can acquire the property and/or chain, but also lease any remaining vacancies or unwanted sites while we also manage the properties for our clients.</p>
                   <p>This unique ability allows Pentz & Partners to fill every real estate related need and coordinate our efforts in achieving our clients goals and objectives.</p>
               </div>

